<!-- PROBLEM -->
<section class="problem" id="problem">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="problem-grid">
      <div>
        <p class="section-eyebrow">The situation</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Someone's wearing the <strong>"data hat"</strong> as a side job.</h2>
        <p class="section-body">Most growing businesses have someone — maybe you — spending a meaningful chunk of their time on reporting and data work they were never hired to do. They're capable. But they're not specialized. And today, the gap between a generalist and someone who does this full-time has never been wider.</p>
        <p class="section-body" style="margin-top:16px;">AI has widened that gap further. The right expertise paired with AI tooling does the work that used to take a small team. You're not paying for hours. You're paying for leverage.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-stat">
        <div class="stat-number"><span class="stat-pct">20</span>%</div>
        <p class="stat-label">of a generalist's time spent on data work costs more than it should — and delivers less than it could.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT I DO -->
<section id="what-i-do">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">What I do</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">One person. <strong>Full-stack data capability.</strong></h2>
    <p class="section-body">I work embedded in your Microsoft environment on an ongoing basis — not parachuting in for a project and disappearing.</p>
    <div class="whatido-grid">
      <div class="whatido-card">
        <svg class="card-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"/></svg>
        <h3 class="card-title">Platform management</h3>
        <p class="card-body">Ongoing stewardship of your Microsoft Fabric, Power BI, and Azure environment — monitoring, governance, capacity optimization, and cost management.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="whatido-card">
        <svg class="card-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg>
        <h3 class="card-title">Reporting & dashboards</h3>
        <p class="card-body">Power BI reports and dashboards that are accurate, fast, and actually used. Built with proper data models and semantic layers — not just pretty charts on bad data.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="whatido-card">
